passages.name: ownershipType
passages.text:
<Message>
  Leier eller eier du leiligheten?
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="type"
          value="RENT"
  >
    [[Jeg leier den->address]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="type"
          value="OWN"
  >
    [[Jeg eier den->address]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: numberCoInsured
passages.text:
<Message>
  Flott! Hvor mange flere vil du at forsikringen skal gjelde for?
</Message>

<Redirect to="[[errorSize]]"
          when="livingSpace > 250"
>
</Redirect>

<Response>
  <when expression="coInsured == 1">
    Meg + {coInsured} annen
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured > 1">
    Meg + {coInsured} andre
  </when>
  <when expression="coInsured == 0">
    Bare meg
  </when>
</Response>

<NumberAction placeholder="2"
              minvalue="0"
              key="coInsured"
              next="[[Fortsett->name]]"
              unit="andre"
>
  <Tooltip>
    <Title>
      Antall medforsikrede
    </Title>
    <Description>
      F.eks partner, barn eller andre du bor med som skal dekkes. Medforsikrede må bo sammen med deg for å bli dekket av forsikringen din
    </Description>
  </Tooltip>
</NumberAction>

passages.name: CreateQuoteError
passages.text: Double-click this passage to edit it.

passages.name: address
passages.text:
<Message>
  Hva er adressen?
</Message>

<Response>
  {street}, {zipCode}
</Response>

<TextActionSet next="[[Fortsett->sizeInput]]">
  <TextAction title="Adresse"
              placeholder="Examplestreet 21"
              large="true"
              key="street"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="Postnummer"
              mask="NorwegianPostalCode"
              placeholder="0123"
              key="zipCode"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: name
passages.text:
<Message>
  Ok! Hva heter du?
</Message>

<Redirect to="[[errorCoInsured]]"
          when="coInsured > 5"
>
</Redirect>

<TextActionSet next="[[Fortsett->birthDate]]">
  <TextAction title="Fornavn"
              placeholder="Hedvig"
              large="true"
              key="firstName"
  >
  </TextAction>
  <TextAction title="Etternavn"
              placeholder="Hedvigsen"
              large="true"
              key="lastName"
  >
  </TextAction>
</TextActionSet>

passages.name: errorCoInsured
passages.text:
<Message>
  Dessverre kan vi bare forsikre hjem med maks 6 personer
</Message>

<Message>
  Meld deg gjerne på vårt nyhetsbrev, så blir du blant de første som får vite det når vi kan forsikre hjem med flere enn 6 personer!
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option>
    [[Ja, jeg vil gjerne motta nyhetsbrev->NewsletterSuccess]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: OfferSuccess
passages.text:
<ExternalRedirect to="Offer">
</ExternalRedirect>

passages.name: currentlyInsured
passages.text:
<Message>
  Har du allerede forsikring en annen annen plass?
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="prevInsurance"
          value="contents"
  >
    [[Ja, jeg har innboforsikring->contentsInsurer]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="prevInsurance"
          value="travel"
  >
    [[Ja, jeg har reiseforsikring->travelInsurer]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="prevInsurance"
          value="contentsAndTravel"
  >
    [[Ja, jeg har både reise- og innboforsikring->contentsAndTravelInsurer]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="prevInsurance"
          value="false"
  >
    [[Nei, jeg har ingen andre forsikringer->email]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: NewsletterSuccess
passages.text: Double-click this passage to edit it.

passages.name: youthEligibilityCheck
passages.text:
<Redirect to="[[Offer]]"
          key="isYouth"
          value="false"
          when="birthDate.Age > 30 || livingSpace > 50 || coInsured > 0"
>
</Redirect>

<Redirect to="[[youth]]"
          when="true"
>
</Redirect>

passages.name: birthDate
passages.text:
<Message>
  Når er du født?
</Message>

<Message>
  Ved å fortsette bekrefter jeg at min personlige data blir håndtert i henhold til GDPR https://www.hedvig.com/no/privacy
</Message>

<Response>
  {birthDate}
</Response>

<TextAction placeholder="dd-mm-åååå"
            mask="BirthDateReverse"
            key="birthDate"
            next="[[Fortsett->currentlyInsured]]"
            unit="Fødselsdato (dd-mm-åååå)"
>
</TextAction>

passages.name: errorSize
passages.text:
<Message>
  Dessverre kan vi foreløpig bare forsikre boliger opp til 250 kvadratmeter
</Message>

<Message>
  Meld deg gjerne på vårt nyhetsbrev, så blir du blant de første som får vite det når vi kan forsikre boliger i den størrelsen du har.
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option>
    [[Ja, jeg vil gjerne motta nyhetsbrev->NewsletterSuccess]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: email
passages.text:
<Message>
  Ok! Fyll inn din epostadresse nedenfor for å komme til ditt prisforslag
</Message>

<TextAction placeholder="your.email@here.now"
            mask="Email"
            key="email"
            next="[[Fortsett->youthEligibilityCheck]]"
>
</TextAction>

passages.name: youth
passages.text:
<Message>
  Bonusspørsmål! Siden du er under 31 år er du kvalifisert for vår ungdomsforsikring med en fast pris på 149 kr/mnd. Høres det bra ut?
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="isYouth"
          value="true"
  >
    [[Ja, jeg vil gjerne ha ungdomsforsikring->Offer]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="isYouth"
          value="false"
  >
    [[Nei, jeg vil ha vanlig forsikring->Offer]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: sizeInput
passages.text:
<Message>
  Hvor mange kvadratmeter er leiligheten?
</Message>

<Response>

</Response>

<NumberAction placeholder="52"

</NumberAction>

passages.name: Offer
passages.text:
<Message>
  Flott, din pris er klar!
</Message>

<GraphQLApi next="[[OfferSuccess]]">
  <Mutation>
    mutation CreateNorwegianCombo(
			$norwegianHomeContentsQuoteId: ID!
			$norwegianTravelQuoteId: ID!
			$firstName: String!
			$lastName: String!
			$birthDate: LocalDate!
			$street: String!
			$zipCode: String!
			$livingSpace: Int!
			$coInsured: Int!
			$isYouth: Boolean!
			$type: NorwegianHomeContentsType!
			$email: String!
			$currentInsurerTravel: String
			$currentInsurerContents: String
		) {
		createNorwegianHomeContentsQuote: createQuote(input: {
		  	id: $norwegianHomeContentsQuoteId,
			firstName: $firstName,
			lastName: $lastName,
			currentInsurer: $currentInsurerContents,
			birthDate: $birthDate,
			norwegianHomeContents: {
			  street: $street
			  zipCode: $zipCode
			  coInsured: $coInsured
			  isYouth: $isYouth
			  livingSpace: $livingSpace
			  type: $type
			}
			email: $email
		  }) {
			... on CompleteQuote {
			  id
			  insuranceCost {
				monthlyGross {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyDiscount {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyNet {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
			  }
			}
		  }
		  createNorwegianTravelQuote: createQuote(input: {
		  	id: $norwegianTravelQuoteId,
			firstName: $firstName,
			lastName: $lastName,
			currentInsurer: $currentInsurerTravel,
			birthDate: $birthDate,
			norwegianTravel: {
			  coInsured: $coInsured
			  isYouth: $isYouth
			}
			email: $email
		  }) {
			... on CompleteQuote {
			  id
			  insuranceCost {
				monthlyGross {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyDiscount {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
				monthlyNet {
				  amount
				  currency
				}
			  }
			}
		  }
  		}
  </Mutation>
  <GeneratedVariable key="norwegianHomeContentsQuoteId"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="norwegianHomeContentsQuoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <GeneratedVariable key="norwegianTravelQuoteId"
                     type="uuid"
                     storeas="norwegianTravelQuoteId"
  >
  </GeneratedVariable>
  <Variable key="firstName"
            from="firstName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="lastName"
            from="lastName"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="currentInsurerTravel"
            from="currentInsurerTravel"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="currentInsurerContents"
            from="currentInsurerContents"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="coInsured"
            from="coInsured"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="birthDate"
            from="birthDate"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="isYouth"
            from="isYouth"
            as="boolean"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="street"
            from="street"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="zipCode"
            from="zipCode"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="livingSpace"
            from="livingSpace"
            as="int"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="type"
            from="type"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Variable key="email"
            from="email"
            as="string"
  >
  </Variable>
  <Error next="[[CreateQuoteError]]">
  </Error>
  <Result key="createNorwegianHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="norwegianContentsMonthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="norwegianContentsMonthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="norwegianContentsMonthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="norwegianContentsMonthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="norwegianContentsMonthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianHomeContentsQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="norwegianContentsMonthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.amount"
          as="norwegianTravelMonthlyGross"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyGross.currency"
          as="norwegianTravelMonthlyGrossCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.amount"
          as="norwegianTravelMonthlyNet"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyNet.currency"
          as="norwegianTravelMonthlyNetCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.amount"
          as="norwegianTravelMonthlyDiscount"
  >
  </Result>
  <Result key="createNorwegianTravelQuote.insuranceCost.monthlyDiscount.currency"
          as="norwegianTravelMonthlyDiscountCurrency"
  >
  </Result>
</GraphQLApi>

passages.name: Start
passages.text:
<Message>
  Hei! La oss gi deg et godt prisforslag. Det tar bare et minutt
</Message>

<Message>
  Vil du ha et prisforslag for din nåværende leilighet eller er du på flyttefot?
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option key="isMover"
          value="false"
  >
    [[Min nåværende leilighet->ownershipType]]
  </Option>
  <Option key="isMover"
          value="true"
  >
    [[Jeg er på flyttefot->ownershipType]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>
